Class TSqlParserBaseVisitor<T>

java.lang.Object
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.AbstractParseTreeVisitor<T>
TSqlParserBaseVisitor<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The return type of the visit operation. Use Void for operations with no return type.
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeVisitor<T>, TSqlParserVisitor<T>
public class TSqlParserBaseVisitor<T>
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.AbstractParseTreeVisitor<T>
implements TSqlParserVisitor<T>
This class provides an empty implementation of TSqlParserVisitor, which can be extended to create a visitor which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
